endCircuit().details: End the circuit, but only the user can do it,  or else remains locked if user doesn't call.

lockCircuit().details: Lock the circuit by sending some ETH.  No forced release mechanism => indefinite lock possible.

devdoc.title: NaiveCircuitChannel Attack Type: Perpetual circuit lock with no forced release

@title NaiveCircuitChannel
 Attack Type: Perpetual circuit lock with no forced release

@dev Lock the circuit by sending some ETH. 
 No forced release mechanism => indefinite lock possible.

@dev End the circuit, but only the user can do it, 
 or else remains locked if user doesn't call.
